WEBVTT

00:00.667 --> 00:08.007
♪

00:08.009 --> 00:09.775
You gotta really
flap 'em hard.

00:11.077 --> 00:12.077
<i>(grunt)</i>

00:12.079 --> 00:13.078
Whoa!

00:13.080 --> 00:14.213
<i>(crash)</i>

00:15.248 --> 00:17.416
Maybe not quite that hard.

00:17.418 --> 00:20.686
♪

00:20.688 --> 00:22.054
Whoa!

00:22.056 --> 00:25.357
Looking good up there,
princess twilight.

00:25.359 --> 00:28.394
Applejack, you know you
don't have to call me that.

00:28.396 --> 00:30.129
Why do you protest so?

00:30.131 --> 00:31.697
You've already given up
wearing your crown

00:31.699 --> 00:35.467
The least you can do
is embrace your new title.

00:35.469 --> 00:37.669
If other ponies want to
address me that way,

00:37.671 --> 00:40.072
I suppose it's fine. But...

00:40.074 --> 00:41.240
Not my friends.

00:41.242 --> 00:43.575
It just doesn't
feel right.

00:43.577 --> 00:49.081
The summer sun celebration
is only two days away

00:49.083 --> 00:51.450
And I'm never going to be
ready to perform my part.

00:51.452 --> 00:54.353
Not if you spend all your
time down here you won't.

00:54.355 --> 00:57.322
Now get up there and show
<u>every</u> pony the big finish!

00:58.558 --> 01:03.462
♪

01:03.464 --> 01:06.298
That's what
I'm talking about!

01:07.200 --> 01:08.500
Waa-hoo!

01:09.736 --> 01:11.136
<i>(scream)</i>

01:11.138 --> 01:12.771
<i>(grunts)</i>

01:13.373 --> 01:14.406
<i>(cough)</i>

01:14.408 --> 01:17.242
<i>(scream)</i>

01:18.445 --> 01:20.112
<i>(zoom)</i>

01:20.114 --> 01:21.613
<i>(scream)</i>

01:23.149 --> 01:24.416
<i>(crash)</i>

01:27.520 --> 01:30.422
Wow! That was a big finish!

01:30.424 --> 01:31.723
<i>(moan)</i>

01:36.262 --> 01:39.798
<i>♪ my little pony,</i>
<i>my little pony ♪</i>

01:39.800 --> 01:41.834
<i>♪ aaaaahhh!</i>

01:41.836 --> 01:46.338
<i>♪ I used to wonder what</i>
<i>friendship could be ♪</i>

01:46.340 --> 01:50.275
<i>♪ until you all shared</i>
<i>its magic with me ♪</i>

01:50.277 --> 01:51.410
<i>♪ big adventure</i>

01:51.412 --> 01:56.682
<i>♪ it's an easy feat</i>

01:56.684 --> 01:59.184
<i>♪ and magic makes it</i>
<i>all complete ♪</i>

01:59.186 --> 02:01.220
<i>♪ my little ponies</i>

02:01.222 --> 02:07.226
<i>♪ do you know you're all</i>
<i>my very best friends? ♪</i>

02:07.228 --> 02:09.528
♪

02:10.763 --> 02:16.401
♪

02:16.403 --> 02:18.403
You look amazing, darling.

02:18.405 --> 02:21.373
They've really captured
your regality.

02:21.375 --> 02:22.608
I suppose.

02:22.610 --> 02:24.576
Don't be so modest.

02:24.578 --> 02:27.312
<i>It's everypony's dream to</i>
<i>someday wear a crown</i>

02:27.314 --> 02:28.780
<i>And have their coronation</i>
<i>ceremony preserved</i>

02:28.782 --> 02:30.449
<i>In stained glass</i>
<i>for all to see.</i>

02:31.484 --> 02:34.219
I don't know if it's
every pony's dream.

02:34.221 --> 02:36.221
Most of my dreams
are about frosting.

02:38.692 --> 02:41.460
We don't want to
miss our train.

02:41.462 --> 02:42.661
Fluttershy's
right.

02:42.663 --> 02:48.200
The official celebration
may be here in canterlot

02:48.202 --> 02:50.435
But whoo-wee! Has the
mayor put us in charge

02:50.437 --> 02:52.271
Of one heck of a
party back home.

02:54.407 --> 02:56.642
Aw, don't look like
that, sugarcube.

02:56.644 --> 02:58.744
You get to be right there
with the other princesses

02:58.746 --> 03:00.646
When celestia
raises the sun.

03:00.648 --> 03:01.513
And I'm honored.

03:01.515 --> 03:03.182
Really I am.

03:03.184 --> 03:04.917
It's just that the
summer sun celebration

03:04.919 --> 03:06.952
Is what first brought
all of us together.

03:06.954 --> 03:08.921
It just doesn't feel right
not getting to spend

03:08.923 --> 03:11.657
Such a special day with
my ponyville friends.

03:11.659 --> 03:14.660
It doesn't feel right
to us either, darling.

03:14.662 --> 03:15.861
If the mayor wasn't
so desperate

03:15.863 --> 03:19.231
We'd most certainly
stay here in canterlot.

03:19.233 --> 03:20.832
<i>And of course we</i>
<i>do understand</i>

03:20.834 --> 03:23.335
<i>That your royal duties</i>
<i>must come first.</i>

03:23.337 --> 03:24.636
The summer sun
celebration

03:24.638 --> 03:26.205
May have brought
us together,

03:26.207 --> 03:27.573
But it's something
much bigger

03:27.575 --> 03:29.675
That'll always
keep us connected.

03:29.677 --> 03:31.777
Exhibit a.

03:31.779 --> 03:33.512
The six of us are
united by the

03:33.514 --> 03:37.916
No amount of "royal duties"
is gonna change that.

03:37.918 --> 03:39.618
Right everypony?

03:39.620 --> 03:40.452
Uh huh!

03:40.454 --> 03:41.653
Mm hm.

03:41.655 --> 03:43.722
Right, pinkie pie?

03:43.724 --> 03:46.491
Creamy, creamy frosting.

03:46.493 --> 03:48.527
<i>(sigh)</i>

03:48.529 --> 03:49.895
You should take
that as a "yes".

03:52.299 --> 03:57.369
It'll be like you're in
ponyville with us!

03:57.371 --> 04:00.639
Unison: Cross my heart
and hope to fly.

04:00.641 --> 04:02.708
Stick a cupcake in my eye.

04:02.710 --> 04:04.243
<i>Rarity: And yu</i>
<i>will be with s</i>

04:04.245 --> 04:05.711
Right after the
celebration.

04:05.713 --> 04:07.379
We already have an
appointment on the books

04:07.381 --> 04:10.382
To discuss the royal
upgrades to your loft decor.

04:10.384 --> 04:13.252
<i>Conductor: All aboard</i>
<i>for ponyville!</i>

04:13.254 --> 04:15.520
<i>(murmurs)</i>

04:17.023 --> 04:17.856
Whee!

04:19.659 --> 04:21.627
<i>(clattering train wheels)</i>

04:21.629 --> 04:24.763
♪

04:24.765 --> 04:26.331
<i>(sigh)</i>

04:26.333 --> 04:27.799
I can't help it, spike.

04:27.801 --> 04:31.536
And I already feel like
I'm missing something.

04:31.538 --> 04:32.804
For the princess.

04:32.806 --> 04:36.408
Dear twilight, you
aren't missing anything.

04:36.410 --> 04:37.876
Your friend, pinkie pie.

04:37.878 --> 04:39.578
<i>Pinkie pie: That's me!</i>

04:39.580 --> 04:42.547
<i>Whoo whee! (laughter)</i>

04:42.549 --> 04:43.949
But I am.

04:47.920 --> 04:51.456
Check. Check. Check. Check.
And... Check.

04:51.458 --> 04:56.328
I credit your extremely
competent assistant.

04:58.332 --> 05:00.732
The celebration isn't
until the day

05:00.734 --> 05:04.336
We could still fit in a
quick trip to ponyville

05:04.338 --> 05:08.507
To finish off these last few
things before the main event.

05:08.509 --> 05:13.779
What if we were delayed
getting back

05:13.781 --> 05:19.451
And then couldn't remember
which things we'd done

05:19.453 --> 05:24.089
What we hadn't done
and what we had done

05:24.091 --> 05:26.858
By not doing the one
really important thing

05:26.860 --> 05:27.993
That we were supposed to do?

05:27.995 --> 05:29.895
<i>(thud)</i>

05:30.630 --> 05:32.664
Uh, so that's a "no", then?

05:32.666 --> 05:34.900
These are the first royal
duties princess celestia

05:34.902 --> 05:37.936
I can't risk
letting her down.

05:37.938 --> 05:40.072
<i>Celestia: And I'm</i>
<i>sure you won't.</i>

05:40.074 --> 05:42.708
♪

05:42.710 --> 05:44.009
Your highness!

05:45.778 --> 05:48.680
No need for that now,
princess twilight.

05:48.682 --> 05:49.681
Sorry.

05:49.683 --> 05:52.351
No need
to apologize.

05:52.353 --> 05:53.518
Sorry.

05:55.355 --> 05:57.756
I must admit that it is
wonderful to actually

05:57.758 --> 06:00.792
Be looking forward to the
summer sun celebration.

06:00.794 --> 06:04.796
For my subjects it has
always been a celebration

06:04.798 --> 06:08.033
Of my defeat of nightmare
moon, but for me?

06:08.035 --> 06:12.571
That I'd had to
banish my own sister.

06:14.040 --> 06:17.042
I guess I'd never really
thought about it that way.

06:17.044 --> 06:19.144
But now it has become a
wonderful reminder

06:19.146 --> 06:22.581
Of her transformation
back into princess luna

06:22.583 --> 06:24.549
And our happy reunion.

06:24.551 --> 06:26.785
I am so pleased that you
will be playing a role

06:26.787 --> 06:28.520
In the festivities.

06:28.522 --> 06:32.557
To see your friends return
to ponyville without you.

06:32.559 --> 06:34.059
Maybe a little.

06:34.061 --> 06:35.694
You may no longer
be my student,

06:35.696 --> 06:37.162
Princess twilight,

06:37.164 --> 06:39.398
But I hope you know that
I will always be here

06:39.400 --> 06:40.832
If you need me.

06:40.834 --> 06:42.734
Just as I hope that you
will always be there

06:42.736 --> 06:43.969
When I need you.

06:44.904 --> 06:46.938
<i>(spike clears his throat)</i>

06:46.940 --> 06:48.507
I think this guy
needs you.

06:48.509 --> 06:50.642
A message for
princess twilight.

06:53.513 --> 06:54.913
<i>(party noisemakers)</i>

06:54.915 --> 06:57.449
A letter from
ponyville, I presume?

06:57.451 --> 06:58.550
Never mind.

06:58.552 --> 06:59.818
It's not important.

06:59.820 --> 07:01.820
Spike, where were we?

07:01.822 --> 07:06.591
We should probably go over
the checklist one more time.

07:06.593 --> 07:08.460
I knew you were
gonna say that.

07:09.562 --> 07:10.862
I'll leave you to it.

07:10.864 --> 07:16.168
<i>(clicking footsteps)</i>

07:16.170 --> 07:18.770
<i>♪ (threatening theme)</i>

07:18.772 --> 07:22.174
<i>(crackling)</i>

07:25.578 --> 07:32.551
<i>(birds chirping)</i>

07:32.553 --> 07:33.218
Huh?

07:33.220 --> 07:36.455
Check. Check. Check. Check.

07:36.457 --> 07:38.457
<i>(stretching groa)</i>

07:38.459 --> 07:40.625
What time is it?

07:40.627 --> 07:42.093
It's the middle
of the night.

07:42.095 --> 07:43.195
But it could
be morning.

07:43.197 --> 07:44.162
That's just it.

07:44.164 --> 07:45.564
I can't tell.

07:47.033 --> 07:49.768
Whoa. That is weird!

07:49.770 --> 07:52.671
We have to find out
what's going on.

07:56.108 --> 07:58.076
<i>(confused murmurs)</i>

07:58.078 --> 07:59.511
What do you
think it means?

08:00.746 --> 08:02.247
Princess twilight
will know.

08:02.249 --> 08:04.883
<i>(excited murmurs)</i>

08:04.885 --> 08:06.785
I'm sure it's just...

08:06.787 --> 08:10.489
Your highness, you
must come with us.

08:13.060 --> 08:17.229
It's princess luna and
princess celestia.

08:17.231 --> 08:18.763
They're gone!

08:18.765 --> 08:19.898
<i>(horrified gasp)</i>

08:24.070 --> 08:26.805
<i>Twilight: But I don't</i>
<i>understand. Where are they?</i>

08:26.807 --> 08:30.108
It seems that princess
celestia and princess luna

08:30.110 --> 08:32.878
... <i>Vanished</i> .

08:32.880 --> 08:34.012
Vanished!

08:34.748 --> 08:37.516
This is why we
have come to you.

08:37.518 --> 08:39.518
We await your command.

08:39.520 --> 08:41.720
My command?

08:41.722 --> 08:44.055
We're officers of
the royal guard.

08:44.057 --> 08:46.157
We take our orders
from royalty.

08:46.159 --> 08:49.027
With princess luna and
princess celestia gone

08:49.029 --> 08:50.695
And princess cadance
overseeing

08:50.697 --> 08:52.197
The crystal empire now,

08:52.199 --> 08:54.666
That means we take our
orders from you.

08:55.669 --> 08:59.304
<i>Princess twilight, there</i>
<i>is no time to waste.</i>

08:59.306 --> 09:01.540
<i>We need to know what</i>
<i>you want us to do.</i>

09:03.576 --> 09:05.677
I want you to continue the
search for princess luna

09:05.679 --> 09:09.681
We have to find them
before ponies start to panic.

09:09.683 --> 09:11.316
There must be some clue
that can tell us

09:11.318 --> 09:12.817
What's happened to them.

09:12.819 --> 09:14.252
If you find
something, anything,

09:14.254 --> 09:15.987
<i>Let me know immediately.</i>

09:18.125 --> 09:21.192
Way to take
charge, twilight.

09:21.194 --> 09:23.995
Your highness, news
from ponyville.

09:23.997 --> 09:27.599
The everfree forest
appears to be, well...

09:27.601 --> 09:28.934
...Invading!

09:28.936 --> 09:30.936
<i>(gasp)</i>

09:30.938 --> 09:33.338
<i>(chittering)</i>

09:33.340 --> 09:36.041
<i>Fluttershy: Excuse</i>
<i>me. Pardon me.</i>

09:36.043 --> 09:37.342
Are you all right?

09:37.344 --> 09:38.877
<i>(chittering)</i>

09:38.879 --> 09:40.211
<i>(bleating sheep)</i>

09:40.213 --> 09:42.681
<i>(low growl)</i>

09:42.683 --> 09:45.083
My goodness, what is it
that has caused you all

09:45.085 --> 09:46.718
Such distress?

09:46.720 --> 09:48.653
<i>(groaning growl)</i>

09:48.655 --> 09:50.822
Whatever it is, I'm
sure it's nothing

09:50.824 --> 09:52.757
You need to really
worry about.

09:52.759 --> 09:53.992
<i>(door opens)</i>

09:53.994 --> 09:55.126
<i>(shrill scream)</i>

09:55.128 --> 09:57.762
<i>♪ (horror sting)</i>

09:57.764 --> 09:58.964
No. You were right.

09:58.966 --> 10:01.733
(whimpering)
very, very worried.

10:05.104 --> 10:07.339
<i>(stretching)</i>

10:07.341 --> 10:10.208
<i>Applejack: Come on, y'all,</i>
<i>put your backs into it.</i>

10:10.210 --> 10:16.815
<i>(stretching)</i>

10:16.817 --> 10:18.116
<i>(chomp)</i>

10:18.118 --> 10:19.618
Nope.

10:19.620 --> 10:21.019
<i>(chomp)</i>

10:21.021 --> 10:22.020
Nope.

10:22.689 --> 10:23.989
<i>(slap)</i>

10:23.991 --> 10:25.056
No.

10:25.058 --> 10:28.159
<i>(grunt)</i>

10:28.161 --> 10:31.329
Dagnabit! We ain't never
seen this kind of trouble

10:31.331 --> 10:33.198
With weeds before.

10:33.200 --> 10:37.202
I've never even seen these
kind of weeds at all!

10:37.204 --> 10:38.203
Have y'all?

10:39.272 --> 10:42.674
Where the heck are these
things comin' from?

10:42.676 --> 10:44.275
<i>(crackling)</i>

10:44.277 --> 10:47.145
And what in tarnation is
going on with the sky?

10:48.848 --> 10:51.216
<i>Rainbow dash: Oh, no</i>
<i>you don't.</i>

10:51.218 --> 10:53.752
This is ponvyille
territory.

10:53.754 --> 10:57.322
<u>After</u> the summer sun
celebration.

10:57.324 --> 10:59.791
You everfree clouds need
to just head on back

10:59.793 --> 11:01.126
To where you belong.

11:02.328 --> 11:03.928
Whoa!

11:05.231 --> 11:07.832
<i>(whoosh)</i>

11:07.834 --> 11:10.669
Gonna make me do this
the hard way, huh?

11:10.671 --> 11:11.803
<i>(za)</i>

11:11.805 --> 11:13.972
<i>(shouts)</i>

11:13.974 --> 11:15.006
Hey!

11:16.008 --> 11:18.009
<i>(crackling)</i>

11:18.011 --> 11:20.211
<i>♪ (cheerful humming)</i>

11:20.213 --> 11:23.348
Hm. Something strange
about the sky.

11:23.350 --> 11:25.116
<i>(crackling)</i>

11:25.118 --> 11:31.756
<i>♪ (eerie)</i>

11:35.795 --> 11:41.132
♪

11:41.134 --> 11:44.703
What in the name of calming
chamomile is going on?

11:44.705 --> 11:45.937
<i>(slurp)</i>

11:46.807 --> 11:50.341
Opal essence,
darling, I'm so sorry.

11:50.343 --> 11:52.811
I promise I'm not doing
this on purpose.

11:53.913 --> 11:54.846
<i>(slurp)</i>

11:54.848 --> 11:56.481
<i>(hiss)</i>

11:57.150 --> 11:58.883
It wasn't me.

11:58.885 --> 11:59.951
I swear.

11:59.953 --> 12:00.985
<i>(growl)</i>

12:03.222 --> 12:05.924
Sweetie belle, if this is
some sort of prank

12:05.926 --> 12:07.992
You and your little crusader
friends are pulling,

12:07.994 --> 12:10.028
I find very little
humor in it.

12:10.030 --> 12:11.830
<i>Sweetie belle: Rarity!</i>
<i>You have to help me.</i>

12:11.832 --> 12:14.032
I think something's
wrong with my horn.

12:14.034 --> 12:14.799
<i>(thud)</i>

12:14.801 --> 12:16.034
<i>(scream)</i>

12:16.036 --> 12:20.939
<i>(high-pitched scream)</i>

12:20.941 --> 12:22.807
<i>♪</i>

12:22.809 --> 12:23.475
<i>(scream)</i>

12:25.044 --> 12:28.146
<i>(galloping hooves)</i>

12:28.148 --> 12:29.781
Where are we going?

12:29.783 --> 12:32.383
The everfree forest
is ... Invading.

12:32.385 --> 12:37.388
And the elements of
harmony to stop it.

12:37.390 --> 12:39.491
I just hope we haven't
missed the train.

12:39.493 --> 12:42.427
Uh, twilight, there
is another way for us

12:42.429 --> 12:44.963
To get to ponyville, remember?

12:44.965 --> 12:45.797
There is?

12:45.799 --> 12:47.232
<i>(grunt)</i>

12:49.101 --> 12:50.235
You can fly.

12:51.036 --> 12:52.871
Oh. Right.

12:54.774 --> 12:56.040
Whoa!

12:56.042 --> 12:57.542
<i>(sputtering engine)</i>

12:57.544 --> 13:01.479
♪

13:01.481 --> 13:03.114
<i>(whoosh)</i>

13:06.552 --> 13:08.286
<i>(panicked screams)</i>

13:08.288 --> 13:10.088
<i>(galloping hooves)</i>

13:10.990 --> 13:12.557
Something very
strange is going on and--

13:12.559 --> 13:13.992
<i>(gasp)</i>

13:15.294 --> 13:17.996
I for one would
appreciate an explanation.

13:17.998 --> 13:20.198
All I know is the
sky's split in two

13:20.200 --> 13:23.301
And these clouds moving in
sure aren't from around here.

13:23.303 --> 13:25.503
<i>Applejack: Neither are all</i>
<i>these crazy plants.</i>

13:27.139 --> 13:29.407
They're comin' from
the everfree forest.

13:29.409 --> 13:31.476
And try as we might,
us earth ponies

13:31.478 --> 13:33.812
Can't do anything
to get rid of 'em.

13:33.814 --> 13:35.213
Don't suppose you
know any magic

13:35.215 --> 13:37.182
That might stop 'em
from spreadin'?

13:37.184 --> 13:39.818
Alas, this whole "raging
forest" situation

13:39.820 --> 13:41.986
Seems to have left my
horn on the fritz.

13:41.988 --> 13:43.488
We have to figure
out something.

13:43.490 --> 13:45.089
I don't know how
much more of this

13:45.091 --> 13:46.090
Ponyville can take.

13:46.092 --> 13:46.858
<i>(sna)</i>

13:46.860 --> 13:50.428
I don't know how
much more  <u>I</u> can take.

13:50.430 --> 13:52.497
<i>Applejack: The forest</i>
<i>is expandin', y'all.</i>

13:52.499 --> 13:54.465
And judgin' by how
fast it's movin',

13:54.467 --> 13:57.368
It doesn't seem content just
takin' over ponyville.

13:57.370 --> 14:00.605
I reckon before long, it'll
cover half of equestria.

14:00.607 --> 14:02.373
♪

14:02.375 --> 14:07.979
<i>(crackling)</i>

14:09.582 --> 14:14.085
♪

14:14.087 --> 14:15.086
Whoa!

14:15.088 --> 14:16.921
<i>(groan)</i>

14:19.392 --> 14:24.529
I'm starting to wish
we'd taken the train!

14:24.531 --> 14:25.597
Almost there.

14:25.599 --> 14:28.266
We need to get the
elements of harmony

14:28.268 --> 14:29.400
And find the others.

14:30.936 --> 14:32.503
Incoming!

14:34.974 --> 14:36.307
Whoa!

14:36.309 --> 14:38.076
<i>(smash)</i>

14:38.078 --> 14:39.210
<i>(thud)</i>

14:42.882 --> 14:44.582
Oh, thank goodness.

14:44.584 --> 14:46.451
Oh, I hope you know we
wouldn't normally

14:46.453 --> 14:48.019
Go through your books
without permission.

14:48.021 --> 14:49.254
<i>(door open)</i>

14:49.256 --> 14:54.025
Sweet, sweet,
wonderful ground.

14:54.027 --> 14:55.593
Ok, I get it!

14:55.595 --> 14:57.395
I need to work
on my flying.

14:57.397 --> 15:01.266
But the everfree forest is
just a teeny-tiny bit

15:01.268 --> 15:02.200
Out of control.

15:02.202 --> 15:03.334
<i>(rattle)</i>

15:03.336 --> 15:04.502
<i>(slam)</i>

15:04.504 --> 15:07.372
Guess it turned out you
were missing something

15:07.374 --> 15:09.908
Here in ponyville
after all.

15:09.910 --> 15:10.909
<i>(crac)</i>

15:11.978 --> 15:15.246
What's causing all
of this calamity?

15:15.248 --> 15:17.181
Has princess celestia
sent you to dispel it

15:17.183 --> 15:18.416
Post haste?

15:18.418 --> 15:20.551
Not exactly.

15:20.553 --> 15:23.254
You see, princess
celestia is,

15:23.256 --> 15:26.658
Well, she and princess
luna are both...

15:26.660 --> 15:28.059
They're missing!

15:28.061 --> 15:30.061
<i>(horrified gasps)</i>

15:30.063 --> 15:33.164
But I've got a hunch
we're going to need

15:33.166 --> 15:35.333
The elements of harmony
to get them back.

15:35.335 --> 15:37.035
Oh yeah.

15:37.037 --> 15:38.603
Just like old times.

15:39.471 --> 15:40.471
<i>(click)</i>

15:42.008 --> 15:43.574
Boo-yah!

15:45.277 --> 15:48.046
I told you we'd always be
connected by the elements.

15:48.048 --> 15:50.214
(sigh) now we just gotta
figure out who to aim

15:50.216 --> 15:53.384
These bad boys at so we can
get celestia and luna back

15:53.386 --> 15:56.487
And keep the rest of equestria
from becoming plant food.

15:56.489 --> 15:57.588
Any ideas?

15:57.590 --> 16:01.059
<i>Pinkie pie:I haven't found</i>
<i>squat in any of the books</i>

16:01.061 --> 16:02.327
<i>I've been looking through.</i>

16:03.228 --> 16:05.229
Oopies. Missed a spot.

16:06.999 --> 16:09.000
Half-day. Half-night.

16:09.002 --> 16:10.535
Strange weather patterns.

16:10.537 --> 16:12.537
Out of control plants.

16:12.539 --> 16:15.373
I think I'm starting to
get a pretty good idea

16:15.375 --> 16:17.308
Of who we're up against.

16:17.310 --> 16:24.749
♪

16:24.751 --> 16:35.293
<i>♪ (rising orchestral)</i>

16:35.295 --> 16:36.761
<i>(zap)</i>

16:36.763 --> 16:43.167
♪

16:44.269 --> 16:45.436
Winter wrap up.

16:45.438 --> 16:47.572
Winter wrap up-- ooooh!

16:47.574 --> 16:51.442
Ho ho! Now twilight,
you know princess celestia

16:51.444 --> 16:53.444
Said that you were to
give me a heads-up

16:53.446 --> 16:57.515
Before you summoned me with
that little spell she gave you.

16:57.517 --> 16:59.117
In case you
haven't noticed,

16:59.119 --> 17:01.119
I was in the middle of
a particularly

17:01.121 --> 17:03.354
Invigorating shower.

17:03.356 --> 17:07.325
Release princess celestia
and princess luna

17:07.327 --> 17:09.627
And stop the everfree
forest from invading!

17:09.629 --> 17:11.429
<i>(crackle)</i>

17:11.431 --> 17:14.799
Why whatever are
you talking about?

17:14.801 --> 17:17.301
Don't you play dumb
with us, discord.

17:17.303 --> 17:19.337
We know you're the one
behind all of this.

17:21.106 --> 17:23.808
Don't get me wrong, I
absolutely love

17:23.810 --> 17:25.643
What you've done
with the place,

17:25.645 --> 17:29.113
But I couldn't possibly
take responsibility.

17:29.115 --> 17:30.281
I'm reformed.

17:30.283 --> 17:31.749
Don't you remember?

17:31.751 --> 17:33.618
Yeah. Right.

17:33.620 --> 17:37.088
This has got your cloven
hoof-prints all over it.

17:37.090 --> 17:40.591
I'll have you know that I
have only one cloven hoof.

17:41.727 --> 17:43.061
<i>(whac)</i>

17:43.063 --> 17:43.828
<i>(poof)</i>

17:43.830 --> 17:45.430
Such accusations.

17:45.432 --> 17:48.066
And here I thought
we were friends.

17:48.068 --> 17:51.269
Drop the act, buster!
We're onto you.

17:51.271 --> 17:54.105
<i>Ladies, ladie,</i>
<i>I'm innocent.</i>

17:54.107 --> 17:56.374
Would I lie to you?

17:56.376 --> 17:57.508
<i>Unision: Yes!</i>

17:57.510 --> 17:59.077
<i>Fluttershy: Um? Maybe?</i>

17:59.079 --> 18:02.780
Well, then, it seems
we've reached an impasse.

18:02.782 --> 18:05.650
I'm telling the truth,
but you think I'm lying.

18:05.652 --> 18:08.119
What do friends like us do
in a situation like this,

18:08.121 --> 18:10.521
Princess twilight?

18:10.523 --> 18:12.790
Congrats by the way
on the promotion.

18:12.792 --> 18:15.359
You totally deserve it.

18:15.361 --> 18:17.829
I say we blast
him back to stone.

18:17.831 --> 18:19.163
Works for me.

18:19.165 --> 18:20.198
Here! Here!

18:21.834 --> 18:24.102
Hey! We can't do that.

18:24.104 --> 18:26.137
What if he really is
telling the truth?

18:27.339 --> 18:29.307
Well, finally!

18:29.309 --> 18:32.643
Somepony willing to give me
the benefit of the doubt.

18:32.645 --> 18:34.378
The rest of you could
learn a lot about

18:34.380 --> 18:36.848
Friendship from my dear
friend, shutterfly here.

18:36.850 --> 18:38.749
Um, it's fluttershy.

18:38.751 --> 18:40.284
Oh, right. Whatever.

18:40.286 --> 18:41.552
If you're not the
one responsible,

18:41.554 --> 18:43.488
Then help us
figure out who is.

18:43.490 --> 18:45.523
I suppose I could,

18:45.525 --> 18:48.392
But after all the hoof-pointing
and besmirching

18:48.394 --> 18:52.630
Of my good name, I just
don't know if I'm up to it.

18:52.632 --> 18:54.398
<i>(needles clicking)</i>

18:54.400 --> 18:58.136
Why don't you ask
your zebra friend

18:58.138 --> 18:59.704
If she knows anything?

18:59.706 --> 19:02.340
<i>♪ (african drums)</i>

19:02.342 --> 19:03.474
Zecora!

19:06.278 --> 19:09.247
From my home,
I've had to flee.

19:09.249 --> 19:12.783
The forest has grown
too wild even for me.

19:12.785 --> 19:15.219
Any idea why all
this is happenin'?

19:15.221 --> 19:18.422
I'm afraid it is a
mystery to me as well.

19:18.424 --> 19:21.392
But I may have
something that,

19:21.394 --> 19:23.261
If combined with a spell...

19:24.630 --> 19:27.465
<i>I do not dare</i>
<i>to use it myself.</i>

19:27.467 --> 19:29.400
<i>The results</i>
<i>would be tragic.</i>

19:29.402 --> 19:32.603
It only responds
to alicorn magic.

19:35.340 --> 19:37.909
Princess twilight, you
can turn the potion

19:37.911 --> 19:40.244
From purple to white.

19:40.246 --> 19:44.348
After a sip you may see
why the sky is day

19:44.350 --> 19:45.650
<u>And</u> night.

19:47.786 --> 19:49.954
<i>(grunt)</i>

19:49.956 --> 19:52.690
<i>(zap)</i>

19:53.659 --> 19:54.892
Oooohhh!

20:00.532 --> 20:06.337
(gulping)

20:08.507 --> 20:09.574
Doesn't seem to be work--

20:09.576 --> 20:11.409
<i>(zap)</i>

20:14.513 --> 20:17.782
<i>♪ (celestial theme)</i>

20:17.784 --> 20:18.716
Where am I?

20:18.718 --> 20:20.985
Not another step.

20:23.255 --> 20:24.956
Princess luna!

20:24.958 --> 20:26.390
I don't understand.

20:26.392 --> 20:29.760
Why did you and
celestia disappear?

20:29.762 --> 20:32.897
Did you really expect me
to sit idly by

20:32.899 --> 20:36.400
While they all basked in
your "precious light"?

20:36.402 --> 20:41.239
There can only be one
princess in equestria.

20:41.241 --> 20:44.609
And that princess
will be me!

20:44.611 --> 20:50.715
<i>(cracking)</i>

20:50.717 --> 20:51.983
<i>(explosion)</i>

20:51.985 --> 20:54.485
♪

20:54.487 --> 20:58.756
<i>(whistling wind)</i>

20:58.758 --> 21:12.970
♪

21:15.874 --> 21:24.482
<i>(maniacal laughter)</i>

21:31.823 --> 21:39.063
♪
